{"tid":1641403,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「攻略」關於中國主權，請指教","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:53:33.000Z","uid":115847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b6dab8830a74b573951fa88da083bb1b10c26c2f","tid":1641403,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"大家好，有個概念想請教大家。<br />\n<br />\n國共內戰之後，<br />\n共產黨成功侵佔大陸既土地，<br />\n而中華民國就由南京搬到台北。<br />\n<br />\n而基於台灣自古以來都屬於中國，<br />\n中華民國一日未被完全徹底殲滅，<br />\n中國既主權都應該歸中華民國所擁有。<br />\n<br />\n而共產黨既角色就好似伊斯蘭國咁，<br />\n非法侵佔完人地既領土之後自稱為國。<br />\n<br />\n如果趁而家中共弱勢，國際社會又咁關注，<br />\n將所有既問題提升到國家主權有無得諗？<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇呢？"},{"pid":"96536451f58fcf3352315eaffe184d278e93ae7c","tid":1641403,"uid":249874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:28:46.000Z","msg":"ISIS無人承認 但CPR以前美帝太心急搞USSR拉攏CPR個陣認咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲拉埋入UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df4123b96ce4324d02ca2b77835408c875645e1","tid":1641403,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96536451f58fcf3352315eaffe184d278e93ae7c","tid":1641403,"uid":249874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:28:46.000Z","msg":"ISIS無人承認 但CPR以前美帝太心急搞USSR拉攏CPR個陣認咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲拉埋入UN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"拉得入就踢得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n或者逐步來，推高台灣國際地位先"},{"pid":"9bbc2b1a3fc1ec0b669fa3f88635200557958996","tid":1641403,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"